# ─── LinkedIn live feed ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# An RSS or JSON URL produced by a third-party LinkedIn aggregator.
# The site fetches this at BUILD TIME only (not in the browser) and bakes
# the latest 6 posts into the static HTML.
#
# Tested with:
#   • RSS.app           https://rss.app/  (RSS XML)
#   • SociableKIT       https://www.sociablekit.com/linkedin-profile-posts-feed/  (JSON or embed)
#   • FetchRSS          https://fetchrss.com/  (RSS XML)
#
# Leave empty to use the curated fallback posts from content/linkedin.ts.
LINKEDIN_FEED_URL=
